# Exploration: paste

## Rounds
  round 0: 5 isolated cumulative, 22 identical in round (single-phase)

## Observed: 3/3 flags
  2 solo, 1 via combination
  robustness: 2 robust, 0 moderate, 0 fragile

Aliases: -d = --delimiters, -s = --serial, -z = --zero-terminated

## Solo (unique behavior)
  -d  # reuse characters from LIST instead of TABs
    exemplar: "-d" "1" "input.txt" "other.txt" in words_minimal (+1441 lines)
    base:
      aardvark	hello world
      abbreviation	
      about	
      abstract	
      accept	
            ...
    flag:
      aardvark1hello world
      abbreviation1
      about1
      abstract1
      accept1
            ...
  -s  # paste one file at a time instead of in parallel
    exemplar: "-s" in words_minimal (different)
    base:
    flag:

## Via combination (distinguishable when paired)
  -z  e.g. (pairwise evidence)

